This product bundles third-party software:

Matt Pocock's skills (https://github.com/mattpocock/skills), licensed under the
MIT License and vendored verbatim under lib/vendor/matt-pocock/. The full licence
text and copyright notice (Copyright (c) 2026 Matt Pocock) are in
lib/vendor/matt-pocock/LICENSE. The skill-maker and plugin-maker skills build on
these files; Kntnt's own conventions on top of them are in lib/skill-conventions.md
and lib/plugin-standard.md.
